<p align="justify">
Student location tracker system is an android application to manage student attendance and inter college mate events on the mobile. In many college teachers use to take attendance and inter college mate participates students details manually. The objective of this project is to add mobility and Automation process. The aim of this app is to track the student location. The system tracks two kinds of location. One is if the student is absences on that day means they find the absence reason place exists or not. Another is the student going to attend the intercollegiate means they can search the location for that college through this track system. It will monitor the student behavior and helps the student and parents to know about the college events. This system gives a prior intimation to the student as soon as his/her attendance goes below the specified Attendance deadline in the form of an SMS alert. This system is related to location services, and second is SMS based which is related to the network services. If Location-based not working then the application uses network-based services which can be able to send and receive messages.
